---
// ユースケースの構文構造と例 — 図解
---

<figure class="uc-diagram" aria-label="ユースケースの構文構造を示す図">
  <div class="uc-diagram__inner">

    <!-- Syntax template -->
    <div class="uc-diagram__syntax">
      <span class="uc-diagram__section-label">構文テンプレート</span>
      <div class="uc-diagram__formula">
        <div class="uc-diagram__token uc-diagram__token--who">
          <span class="uc-diagram__token-bracket">〈</span>誰<span class="uc-diagram__token-bracket">〉</span>が
        </div>
        <div class="uc-diagram__formula-sep" aria-hidden="true">·</div>
        <div class="uc-diagram__token uc-diagram__token--what">
          <span class="uc-diagram__token-bracket">〈</span>何<span class="uc-diagram__token-bracket">〉</span>を
        </div>
        <div class="uc-diagram__formula-sep" aria-hidden="true">·</div>
        <div class="uc-diagram__token uc-diagram__token--action">
          <span class="uc-diagram__token-bracket">〈</span>行動<span class="uc-diagram__token-bracket">〉</span>できる
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="uc-diagram__roles">
        <div class="uc-diagram__role">
          <span class="uc-diagram__role-name">ユーザーペルソナ</span>
          <span class="uc-diagram__role-note">主語</span>
        </div>
        <div class="uc-diagram__role-spacer" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="uc-diagram__role">
          <span class="uc-diagram__role-name">概念オブジェクト</span>
          <span class="uc-diagram__role-note">目的語 / モノ</span>
        </div>
        <div class="uc-diagram__role-spacer" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="uc-diagram__role">
          <span class="uc-diagram__role-name">タスク</span>
          <span class="uc-diagram__role-note">動詞 / コト</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="uc-diagram__divider" aria-hidden="true">↓</div>

    <!-- Example -->
    <div class="uc-diagram__example">
      <span class="uc-diagram__section-label">記述例</span>
      <div class="uc-diagram__example-row">
        <span class="uc-diagram__ex-token uc-diagram__ex-token--who">〈購入者〉</span>
        <span class="uc-diagram__ex-particle">が</span>
        <span class="uc-diagram__ex-token uc-diagram__ex-token--what">〈購入履歴〉</span>
        <span class="uc-diagram__ex-particle">を</span>
        <span class="uc-diagram__ex-token uc-diagram__ex-token--action">〈閲覧〉</span>
        <span class="uc-diagram__ex-particle">できる</span>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
  <figcaption class="uc-diagram__caption">
    機能一覧ではなく「用途の文」で定義することで、何を作るべきかの意図がチーム全体で揃う。
  </figcaption>
</figure>

<style>
  .uc-diagram {
    margin-block: 2.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    background: linear-gradient(
      160deg,
      color-mix(in oklch, var(--surface) 80%, white),
      var(--surface)
    );
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .uc-diagram__inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0;
    padding: 1.75rem 1.5rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .uc-diagram__section-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.67rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-faint);
    margin-block-end: 0.85rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* Syntax block */
  .uc-diagram__syntax {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 32rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: var(--bg);
    padding: 1.1rem 1.25rem 1rem;
  }

  .uc-diagram__formula {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-block-end: 0.9rem;
  }

  .uc-diagram__token {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    line-height: 1.3;
    padding: 0.18rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
  }

  .uc-diagram__token-bracket {
    color: var(--text-faint);
  }

  .uc-diagram__token--who {
    color: var(--accent-deep);
    background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--accent-wash) 70%, transparent);
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in oklch, var(--accent) 25%, transparent);
  }

  .uc-diagram__token--what {
    color: var(--text);
    background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--surface) 60%, var(--bg));
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .uc-diagram__token--action {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--surface) 60%, var(--bg));
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .uc-diagram__formula-sep {
    color: var(--text-faint);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    padding-inline: 0.1rem;
  }

  .uc-diagram__roles {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-around;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding-block-start: 0.75rem;
    border-block-start: 1px dashed var(--border);
  }

  .uc-diagram__role {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.2rem;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .uc-diagram__role-spacer {
    width: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    align-self: stretch;
  }

  .uc-diagram__role-name {
    font-size: 0.76rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .uc-diagram__role-note {
    font-size: 0.66rem;
    color: var(--text-faint);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* Divider arrow */
  .uc-diagram__divider {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--accent-dim);
    line-height: 1;
    padding-block: 0.4rem;
  }

  /* Example block */
  .uc-diagram__example {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 32rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--accent-wash) 50%, var(--bg));
    padding: 1.1rem 1.25rem 1rem;
  }

  .uc-diagram__example-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.1rem 0.25rem;
  }

  .uc-diagram__ex-token {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    padding: 0.1rem 0.4rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
  }

  .uc-diagram__ex-token--who {
    color: var(--accent-deep);
    background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--accent-wash) 80%, transparent);
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in oklch, var(--accent) 30%, transparent);
  }

  .uc-diagram__ex-token--what {
    color: var(--text);
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
  }

  .uc-diagram__ex-token--action {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
  }

  .uc-diagram__ex-particle {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--text-faint);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Caption */
  .uc-diagram__caption {
    padding: 0.55rem 1.5rem 0.6rem;
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    color: var(--text-faint);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    border-block-start: 1px solid var(--border);
    text-align: center;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  @media (max-width: 520px) {
    .uc-diagram__formula {
      gap: 0.15rem;
    }

    .uc-diagram__token {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .uc-diagram__roles {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 0.4rem;
    }

    .uc-diagram__role-spacer {
      display: none;
    }

    .uc-diagram__role {
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
